MESSAGE.value: Minor refactoring, update to use Vaadin 7.7.0 - namespace change: conversion -> data-binding - Comment update
Refactoring - Updated menu-item to use clojure.spec to parse arguments - Updated clojure to 1.9.0_alpha11
Refactoring - Updated widget creation to use clojure.spec to parse arguments
Builder extension and fixes - Added upload builder and Upload event handlers - Refactoring: better synthetic option handling - Bug fixes: Sampler, TableColumn children validation
Various changes: - Bug fix: buildable-children ignored TableColumns - More Sampler restyling
Various changes: - Updated Changelog - Release build script added
Updated build script to save docs along with the uberjars
Various changes: - Build scripts update - Better doc strings - Added validation to docs
Added Action creation and attachment, plus various: - LoginForm moved to ui namespace - Bug fixes in synthetic config option validation
Bug fix in commit observer - Commit errors now handled without killing the observer
Bug fix in config.clj - now accept nil as argument to zero-arg setter
Bug fixes: - Incorrect LoginForm ref in config-gen - Bad child spec for components
